00:02.585 --> 00:06.472
My name is Drew and we are so glad that all of you chose to be with us here today.

00:06.492 --> 00:08.555
I want to invite all of you to stay and join us.

00:08.996 --> 00:17.831
And whether you are here in the room or joining us online, we believe something really powerful happens when we gather as a group of people and sing the songs that we're going to sing today.

00:18.271 --> 00:24.402
These words remind us of the goodness and faithfulness of a God who loves us and a God who is for us.

00:24.442 --> 00:26.345
